{"tid":138516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事隔半年特府終改口　取消磁能線Znaps獎項","createTime":"2017-02-28T16:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T01:41:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e58fc35b3b0fad44921be634da62b160b47ecc2","tid":138516,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170228/large/1488292759_62a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170228%2Flarge%2F1488292759_62a8.jpg&h=aa38395f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年《蘋果》踢爆，「磁能線」Znaps於眾籌網站Kickstarter推出「磁能線」集資1800萬元後擬似走數，遲遲未發貨，其後更以香港公司Znaps Limited（施納士）名義，獲港府頒發「香港資訊及通訊科技獎」初創企業銅獎。政府今日宣佈，資訊科技總監辦公室在諮詢「香港資訊及通訊科技獎」督導委員會後，決定取消Znaps Limited的得獎資格。<br />\n<br />\n去年《蘋果》揭發，以走數「聞名」的眾籌項目智能咖啡機，其主事人趙公允的妻子劉志芳，原來正是Znaps的幕後話事人，去年底更以香港公司Znaps Limited名義，奪得政府主辦的香港資訊及通訊科技獎獎項，觸發違規參賽疑團，惟當局調查近月後，最終決定「放生」該公司，拒撤回獎項。<br />\n<br />\n事隔半年，資科辦表示，在檢視所有資料及聽取督委會的意見後，認為Znaps Limited未能完全符合參賽資格，尤其有關「產品須已推出巿場最少三個月」的規定。故此，資科辦決定取消其得奬資格。<br />\n<br />\n政府又指，「2017香港資訊及通訊科技獎」，資科辦已落實改善措施，加強檢視參賽項目、籌辦機構核實參賽資格的程序和評審工作。資科辦會繼續與各界合作，透過這個廣受認同的專業獎項，促進本地資訊及通訊科技業的發展。"},{"pid":"6afaf1b910bf973e40880f0d81fba95cbddd09df","tid":138516,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170228&amp;guid=56367744&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170228%26guid%3D56367744%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=4c652f13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170228%26guid%3D56367744%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=029325db\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170228&amp;guid=56367744&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"5f6dce00cc6baffee91a9c3579d81d17a1798fca","tid":138516,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca9e1d1ecead4249140bd303ba8d4457724c5f1","tid":138516,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"香港科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46dbc558a5778ef49e7518b641753001313aff6d","tid":138516,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"錢已袋話知你<br />\n反正香港人最善忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2765a6ff990bc87672a0d9c3cfe8c6c5fdb3170","tid":138516,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T20:22:08.000Z","msg":"其主事人趙公允的妻子劉志芳，原來正是Znaps的幕後話事人<br />\n<br />\n根本係同一個積犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名睇踩港撚入嚟表演"},{"pid":"d73c4e3ee26c2f1054a34dc06ee3e73b2e42514d","tid":138516,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}